{"tid":1119741,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"唔多覺，已經grad左一年","createTime":"2019-04-22T07:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T16:02:31.000Z","uid":71376,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"96ffb9c9fb5f93efea8571e3f45b87372fe98cac","tid":1119741,"uid":71376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:00:14.000Z","msg":"睇番上年呢個時候差唔多係大學既last teaching day，grad左一年既你宜家過成點？<br />\n<br />\n我先，日日做狗，忙到pk，仲要係忙完都唔知自己忙過啲咩個隻"},{"pid":"a87bfef35e557c0d1a8ae7cf9c9d8122043f5969","tid":1119741,"uid":123308,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:02:55.000Z","msg":"以前 book 時間 make appointments 睇專科，拎嘢去維修等等好容易，一係冇堂上，一係就走堂<br />\n<br />\n而家？好難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特別自己做緊呢行冇 annual leave"},{"pid":"a68b71f2d3bc097e0b3cb6041a9d956d385b8558","tid":1119741,"uid":42217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:03:04.000Z","msg":"聽朝準時返工"},{"pid":"8d2ffe0d16a54f333dc12f22265b986677fe7c91","tid":1119741,"uid":172009,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:05:17.000Z","msg":"未grad 但係好驚 唔想面對社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fc7a9a294ed2f6afa68f7e44ed00d2bf319c932","tid":1119741,"uid":71376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a87bfef35e557c0d1a8ae7cf9c9d8122043f5969","tid":1119741,"uid":123308,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:02:55.000Z","msg":"以前 book 時間 make appointments 睇專科，拎嘢去維修等等好容易，一係冇堂上，一係就走堂<br />\n<br />\n而家？好難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 特別自己做緊呢行冇 annual leave"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:07:23.000Z","msg":"教書？<br />\n<br />\n我都覺宜家冇哂私人時間<br />\n我本身住大西北，市區番工，每日來回差唔多3個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以宜家好有動力要搬出市區"},{"pid":"c9f387d17371af674e123d8e9b7b40a58fc59b85","tid":1119741,"uid":59648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:07:32.000Z","msg":"都係上年grad, 話咁快就1年<br />\n呢一年都係做住非本科嘅工先，嚟緊會轉去第二行，重新開始"},{"pid":"a4202bafa95f00583dfc950bc27ba23207f3824b","tid":1119741,"uid":71376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d2ffe0d16a54f333dc12f22265b986677fe7c91","tid":1119741,"uid":172009,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:05:17.000Z","msg":"未grad 但係好驚 唔想面對社會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:58:54.000Z","msg":"出到黎你就會發覺唔到你唔成長<br />\n呢樣嘢唔洗驚，反正幾辛苦都好，捱下捱下就會捱過"},{"pid":"db9351e0fbb2de59673f31d0d0a4e9b3824d9c6a","tid":1119741,"uid":84781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T02:54:33.000Z","msg":"又老左一年，但個人無進步過，日日準時番工無咩目標咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/south_bear.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75911dd65b1aec869ef9f0c50b9f76bc6306b2ac","tid":1119741,"uid":90946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:00:51.000Z","msg":"日日就係逼車返工，然後ot，放工食飯，食完飯hea陣沖涼訓教又再loop <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做左一年都無加過人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係時候轉工"},{"pid":"e04780a35fdad68cd8fb8520cd24a8f376ba68a3","tid":1119741,"uid":41975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:00:55.000Z","msg":"好想轉工 但又好似好掙扎想挨夠一年先轉...<br />\n人工又低 做既野雖然唔係好辛苦 但係真係好似無乜前途<br />\n對於安穩過一世黎講而家呢份工係好正既...<br />\n好想跳入勁既公司做....唉"},{"pid":"9cca63accbf74830ff1018ccab9f5bdb1584f05f","tid":1119741,"uid":89287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T03:06:50.000Z","msg":"就黎返夠一年 屋企附近返工 搭來回一個鐘左右 收工自己有PT<br />\n日日準時收工放工 年年等跳POINT 加雞碎咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{